    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add the <strong>diced shallot, ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground allspice</strong>,<strong> half</strong> of the <strong>smoked paprika</strong> (you'll use the rest later!),<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> flour </strong>and the <strong>cayenne pepper </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook for a further 1-2 min</p>",
